(The system implements four tiers of authentication:) Tj
T* (1. MINISTRY_REP: Can submit new requisitions and edit their group's entries while in draft stage.) Tj
T* (2. APPROVER_L1: General committee verifiers. Inspects quotes, compares bids, and pushes to Level 2. ) Tj
T* (3. APPROVER_L2: Senior treasury officers. Checks funding pools, marks final authorization status.) Tj
T* (4. SUPER_ADMIN: Global system configurations, adding new groups, manual ledger adjustments, and member) Tj
T* (status edits.) Tj
ET
